We welcome Interstate and country buyers and can organise vehicle transport for you if required. Need to drive away today? We have competitive on-site bank finance with on the spot approval through Australia’s leading lenders. (Conditions apply, to approved purchasers only.)
We also provide 3 year Extended Warranties with Roadside assist and also discounted Car Insurance. 
Have a vehicle to trade in? We have our own dedicated vehicle appraisers, who can value your vehicle and get you top dollars.

Guaranteed clear title (PPSR).

Specifications have been sourced from redbook.com.au and are based on manufacturer standard specifications. Actual specifications for this vehicle may differ, please confirm with the seller.
